OL,4,CHorizon victims could go on for years
OL,5,C` lawyers
OL,7,FThe "retraumatising" compensation
OL,8,Fprocess for subpostmasters wronged by
OL,9,Fthe Post Office Horizon scandal could
OL,10,Fgo on for another three years, lawyers
OL,11,Fhave warned.
OL,13,FMany victims of the scandal are still
OL,14,Fawaiting full redress, as one of the
OL,15,Ffinal reports from the long-running
OL,16,Finquiry ` looking at the impact on
OL,17,Fthose who had their lives destroyed
OL,18,Fand compensation ` is set to be
OL,19,Fpublished on Tuesday.
