OL,7,FMore than 900 subpostmasters were
OL,8,Fwrongfully prosecuted by the Post
OL,9,FOffice between 1999 and 2015 after
OL,10,Ffaulty Horizon software made it look
OL,11,Fas though money was missing from their
OL,12,Faccounts.
OL,14,FThe previous Conservative government
OL,15,Fsaid those who had their convictions
OL,16,Fquashed were eligible for #600,000
OL,17,Fpayouts ` with victims such as Amanda
OL,18,Fand Norman Barber accepting the fixed
OL,19,Foffer.
