OL,7,FDespite losing their business and
OL,8,Fhome, the Warrington couple said they
OL,9,Ffound it "almost impossible" to
OL,10,Fprovide the details required to have
OL,11,Ftheir case individually assessed so
OL,12,Fdid not want to risk "getting less".
OL,14,FUnexplained shortfalls in their
OL,15,Faccounts at Thelwall Post Office
OL,16,Feventually led to them being
OL,17,Fprosecuted over a deficit of #5,600 `
OL,18,Fdespite using around #200,000 of their
OL,19,Fown money to attempt to balance the
OL,20,Fbooks.
