OL,7,FBoth received a community order of 12
OL,8,Fmonths and 100 hours' community
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FSpeaking about the redress process,
OL,12,FAmanda, 55, said: "We were being asked
OL,13,Fto produce evidence we simply couldn't
OL,14,Fget our hands on with regards to our
OL,15,Flosses as we are talking going back 15
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,F"We found it almost impossible to
OL,19,Fprovide the details needed to go down
OL,20,Fthe route of having our case
OL,21,Findividually assessed.
