OL,7,F"It just didn't seem worth it. I think
OL,8,Fsubpostmasters are still being left in
OL,9,Fan impossible situation when it comes
OL,10,Fto seeking true and full redress.
OL,12,F"Given the time it would take we
OL,13,Fsimply couldn't risk a full assessment
OL,14,Fand getting less, particularly because
OL,15,Fthe lack of documents we had.
OL,17,F"It got to the stage where, when the
OL,18,F#600,000 was offered, it seemed the
OL,19,Fbest way to bring years of torture to
OL,20,Fan end."
