OL,7,FRedress has been a key issue for
OL,8,Fsubpostmasters since the scandal came
OL,9,Fto light, with many finding the
OL,10,Fvarious compensation schemes difficult
OL,11,Fto navigate.
OL,13,FLead campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,14,Fpreviously described the various
OL,15,Fprocesses as "quasi-kangaroo courts",
OL,16,Ftelling The Sunday Times that the
OL,17,FDepartment for Business and Trade
OL,18,F"sits in judgment of the claims and
OL,19,Falters the goal posts as and when it
OL,20,Fchooses".
