OL,7,FThe chairman of the Horizon IT
OL,8,Finquiry, Sir Wyn Williams, is due to
OL,9,Fpublish his findings on redress on
OL,10,FTuesday, with Amanda Barber saying she
OL,11,Fwill join other subpostmasters in
OL,12,Fattending the report's publication
OL,13,Fevent.
OL,15,FShe said: "We feel we just need to be
OL,16,Fthere to hear what is said.
OL,18,F"Lives were ruined and compensation
OL,19,Fhas been made too hard to get, and too
OL,20,Flittle by far."
