OL,7,FOne law firm involved in securing
OL,8,Fredress for victims, Hudgell
OL,9,FSolicitors, said it still had more
OL,10,Fthan 700 ongoing compensation cases to
OL,11,Fresolve.
OL,13,FSolicitor Neil Hudgell said the firm
OL,14,Fhad agreed damages for more than 300
OL,15,Fpeople, totalling #170 million, but
OL,16,Fsaid the redress process had "far too
OL,17,Fmuch red tape to get through".
