OL,7,FHe said: "We have seen inconsistencies
OL,8,Fbetween the various compensation
OL,9,Fschemes, which remain over-engineered
OL,10,Fand over-legalistic, with far too much
OL,11,Fred tape to get through.
OL,13,F"There has also been a repeated
OL,14,Ffailure to give the benefit of the
OL,15,Fdoubt to subpostmasters in appropriate
OL,16,Fcircumstances.
OL,18,F"It's made it far too long a process
OL,19,Ffor so many people who have been
OL,20,Fthrough so much, and are now in the
OL,21,Flatter stages of their lives.
