OL,7,F"It has been retraumatising for many,
OL,8,Fand increasing numbers are sadly
OL,9,Fpassing away without seeing redress."
OL,11,FAddressing how long it could take for
OL,12,Fall claims to be settled, the
OL,13,Fsolicitor added: "At the current
OL,14,Fspeed, we are looking at another two
OL,15,Fto three years."
OL,17,FMr Hudgell said one client who was
OL,18,Finitially offered #50,000 has seen
OL,19,Ftheir offer rise to #500,000.
