OL,7,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade said: "We are
OL,9,Fgrateful for the inquiry's work, which
OL,10,Fhas revealed the immeasurable
OL,11,Fsuffering that victims of the scandal
OL,12,Fhave endured.
OL,14,F"This Government has quadrupled the
OL,15,Ftotal amount paid to affected
OL,16,Fpostmasters to provide them with full
OL,17,Fand fair redress, with more than #1
OL,18,Fbillion having now been paid to over
OL,19,F7,300 claimants."
